Class AbstractJsonSerializer

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.logspace.agent.api.json.AbstractJsonSerializer

    AgentControllerCapabilitiesJsonSerializer, AgentControllerDescriptionJsonSerializer, AgentControllerOrdersJsonSerializer, EventJsonSerializer, EventPageJsonSerializer

    public abstract class AbstractJsonSerializer
extends Object
    Base class for JSON serializers. Simplifies handling of the JsonGenerator.
